article_title: Onslow Memorial Hospital pursues possible partnership

article_metadata.description: Onslow Memorial Hospital sent seven requests for proposal to undisclosed recipients last month to alleviate the independent nonprofit’s financial pinch that health care officials say has clasped clinics in the United States as the complete Affordable Care Act is enacted.
article_metadata.author: Michael Todd - Michael.Todd@JDNews.com
